  "title": "ISic003424. Epitaph of Lamnos Kornelios Alkinon",
  "body": "<div id=\"editions\"><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag; edition source: autopsy Prag 2014-09-10</div><div id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"grc\">  <div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  <a id=\"al1-interpretive\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Λαμνα · Κορ\n                    νηλι · Ἀλκίνων\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Λαμνα\"><span data-text=\"Λαμνα\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"Λάμνη\">Λαμνα</span></span> · <span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Κορ\n                    νηλι\"><span data-text=\"Κορ\n                    νηλι\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"Κορνηλία\">Κορ-<br id=\"al2-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span>νηλι</span></span> · <span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ἀλκίνων\"><span data-text=\"Ἀλκίνων\" data-n=\"25\" data-lemma=\"Ἀλκίνων\">Ἀλκίνων</span></span></span>  <br id=\"al3-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span><span data-text=\"χρηστὲ\" data-n=\"30\" data-lemma=\"χρηστός\">χρηστὲ</span>  <span data-text=\"χαῖρε\" data-n=\"35\" data-lemma=\"χαίρω\">χαῖρε</span>  <br id=\"al4-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span><span data-text=\"ἔζησεν\" data-n=\"40\" data-lemma=\"ζῶ\">ἔζησεν</span> · <span data-text=\"ἔτη\" data-n=\"50\" data-lemma=\"ἔτος\">ἔτη</span>  <br id=\"al5-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">5</span>❦ <span data-text=\"λβ\" data-n=\"60\" data-lemma=\"λβ\">λβ</span>´ ❦ </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Dmitry Dundua, Robert Crellin</div><div id=\"edition-interpretive-simple-lemmatized\">  <div class=\"textpart\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  <span data-text=\"Λαμνα\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"Λάμνη\">Λαμνα</span>  <span data-text=\"Κορνηλι\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"Κορνηλία\">Κορνηλι</span>  <span data-text=\"Ἀλκίνων\" data-n=\"25\" data-lemma=\"Ἀλκίνων\">Ἀλκίνων</span>  <span data-text=\"χρηστὲ\" data-n=\"30\" data-lemma=\"χρηστός\">χρηστὲ</span>  <span data-text=\"χαῖρε\" data-n=\"35\" data-lemma=\"χαίρω\">χαῖρε</span>  <span data-text=\"ἔζησεν\" data-n=\"40\" data-lemma=\"ζῶ\">ἔζησεν</span>  <span data-text=\"ἔτη\" data-n=\"50\" data-lemma=\"ἔτος\">ἔτη</span>  <span data-text=\"λβ\" data-n=\"60\" data-lemma=\"λβ\">λβ</span>  </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag; edition source: autopsy Prag 2014-09-10</div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\"><div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><a id=\"al1-diplomatic\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Λαμνα · Κορ\n                    νηλι · Ἀλκίνων\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Λαμνα\"><span data-text=\"Λαμνα\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"Λάμνη\">ΛΑΜΝΑ</span></span>·<span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Κορ\n                    νηλι\"><span data-text=\"Κορ\n                    νηλι\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"Κορνηλία\">ΚΟΡ<br id=\"al2-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span>ΝΗΛΙ</span></span>·<span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ἀλκίνων\"><span data-text=\"Ἀλκίνων\" data-n=\"25\" data-lemma=\"Ἀλκίνων\">ΑΛΚΙΝΩΝ</span></span></span><br id=\"al3-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span><span data-text=\"χρηστὲ\" data-n=\"30\" data-lemma=\"χρηστός\">ΧΡΗΣΤΕ</span><span data-text=\"χαῖρε\" data-n=\"35\" data-lemma=\"χαίρω\">ΧΑΙΡΕ</span><br id=\"al4-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span><span data-text=\"ἔζησεν\" data-n=\"40\" data-lemma=\"ζῶ\">ΕΖΗΣΕΝ</span>·<span data-text=\"ἔτη\" data-n=\"50\" data-lemma=\"ἔτος\">ΕΤΗ</span><br id=\"al5-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">5</span>❦<span data-text=\"λβ\" data-n=\"60\" data-lemma=\"λβ\">ΛΒ</span>❦</span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Dmitry Dundua, Robert Crellin</div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic-simple-lemmatized\"><div class=\"textpart\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><span data-text=\"Λαμνα\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"Λάμνη\">ΛΑΜΝΑ</span><span data-text=\"Κορνηλι\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"Κορνηλία\">ΚΟΡΝΗΛΙ</span><span data-text=\"Ἀλκίνων\" data-n=\"25\" data-lemma=\"Ἀλκίνων\">ΑΛΚΙΝΩΝ</span><span data-text=\"χρηστὲ\" data-n=\"30\" data-lemma=\"χρηστός\">ΧΡΗΣΤΕ</span><span data-text=\"χαῖρε\" data-n=\"35\" data-lemma=\"χαίρω\">ΧΑΙΡΕ</span><span data-text=\"ἔζησεν\" data-n=\"40\" data-lemma=\"ζῶ\">ΕΖΗΣΕΝ</span><span data-text=\"ἔτη\" data-n=\"50\" data-lemma=\"ἔτος\">ΕΤΗ</span><span data-text=\"λβ\" data-n=\"60\" data-lemma=\"λβ\">ΛΒ</span></span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div></div>  <div id=\"facsimile-images\"><h2>Facsimile Images</h2><a href=\"ISic003424_tiled.tif\"><img title=\"Photo J. Prag, 2014-09-10, by permission of Museo Archeologico Regionale Paolo Orsi\" src=\"ISic003424_tiled-thumb.tif\"></a><a href=\"ISic003424.jpg\"><img title=\"Photo J. Prag, 2014-09-10, by permission of Museo Archeologico Regionale Paolo Orsi\" src=\"ISic003424-thumb.jpg\"></a><a href=\"ISic003424_rear_tiled.tif\"><img title=\"Photo J. Prag, 2014-09-10, by permission of Museo Archeologico Regionale Paolo Orsi\" src=\"ISic003424_rear_tiled-thumb.tif\"></a><a href=\"ISic003424_rear.jpg\"><img title=\"Photo J. Prag, 2014-09-10, by permission of Museo Archeologico Regionale Paolo Orsi\" src=\"ISic003424_rear-thumb.jpg\"></a></div>  <div id=\"apparatus\"><h4>Apparatus criticus</h4><ul><li><span>  <span>Text from autopsy</span>  </span></li></ul></div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2>English translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\"><a href=\"http://orcid.org/0000-0003-3819-8537\">Jonathan Prag</a></p>  <p>Farewell worthy Lamnos Kornelios Alkinon. He lived 32 years.</p>  </div>  <div id=\"commentary\"><h2>commentary</h2>  <p>  </p></div>  <div id=\"bibliography\"><h2>bibliography</h2>  <ul><li> Orsi NSA 1907 494 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001392\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001392</a>  </li></ul>  <ul><li> Libertini 1926 17 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001874\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001874</a>  </li></ul>  </div>  <div id=\"handnote\"> <p>Letters are deeply v-cut, somewhat elongated, and showing some tendency towards curvature in e.g. the M. Minial use of serifs. Lunate omega, but rectilinear epsilon and sigma. Alpha with broken bar; mu with four full-length, slanting strokes; kappa with short ams; omicron ovoid but full height; epsilon tall and thin, all bars of equal length; zeta an equal length Z. Use of interpunct to mark off the names, and hedera around the numeral.</p> Line 1  29-38  Line 2  25-30  Line 3-5  30-34  Interlineation line 1 to 2    </div><div id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. </div>",
